    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Step into a twisted 80s-inspired world full of dark secrets, haunted graveyards, and   supernatural threats. Travel trough the board and explore the different areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037040/extras/68871977868c182af98cf32065bcf8e9.poster.avif?t=1763546560\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037040/extras/68871977868c182af98cf32065bcf8e9.webm?t=1763546560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037040/extras/68871977868c182af98cf32065bcf8e9.mp4?t=1763546560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037040/extras/608730e04d4f437f47b874ba7b9addf6.webp?t=1763546560\" width=614 height=60 /></span> Battle your way through the board. The tougher the foe, the better the rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037040/extras/a576fdff8f983239f44df6f032556942.webp?t=1763546560\" width=614 height=60 /></span> Trick, trap, or take them down... but beware, they’ll do the same to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037040/extras/57fa208674e8c60021040c2082cb9905.webp?t=1763546560\" width=614 height=60 /></span> Hunt down hidden crystals across the board. No crystals, no final fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037040/extras/83ef4261e50a8b822b1afc37e654b36d.webp?t=1763546560\" width=614 height=60 /></span> Only one can claim victory. Will you have the most crystals? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiplayer PVP</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiplayer PVE</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Boardgame aesthetics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Crossplay (IOS/Android/PC)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Horror satirical elements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Turn-based gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Original music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Custom cards and boardgame </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Skin customization </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Tabletop vibes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiple levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dynamic optimization of game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > P2P hosting solution</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiple Events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > In-game tutorial</p></li></ul>",
